                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-expand" id="expand-5380c86" style="display:none">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>A contingency budget is an additional reserve (usually 10-20% of the
                                            total cost) for unexpected expenses.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-wrapper ">
                                <div class="card-header">
