                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>This depends on your goals, location, and budget. For example, wood
                                            is great for aesthetics, while steel is strong and durable.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-wrapper ">
                                <div class="card-header">
